{"tid":391380,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"中意好耐既女仔比人溝左了","createTime":"2017-09-07T17:25:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-09T05:43:41.000Z","uid":90178,"like":60,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fd2f63920625bf55faa580258407fd095ce9028c","tid":391380,"uid":90178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T17:25:34.000Z","msg":"大學入面識，佢大我兩年。大家一齊既時間唔係好多，但都有去過行街睇戲，玩過煮飯仔，試過飲酒飲到醉哂，仲有D瑣碎回憶一直存在係腦海中。<br />\n佢唔係d咩女神type, 小小肥矮矮地，但係我心目中係一個好可愛既女仔。其實佢都知道我既心意，然而個&mdash;刻佢認為我唔夠成熟，結果無法去到戀人關係。<br />\n更甚者，佢早我兩年時間入左間大公司做，當中識左好多人，包括佢既男朋友。今日先知原來追到佢既係佢 senior, 大佢幾年。只恨自己無能為力，眼白白睇住自己最心愛最想守護既人比其他人搶走，個種無力感，比死更難受。"},{"pid":"c460f94c05d2040afa3a742a28bd701bb6245eae","tid":391380,"uid":144607,"like":2,"dislike":36,"score":-34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T17:28:04.000Z","msg":"大你兩年，就算俾你地一齊左，都好難一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f63bc2bccd6980bf7bbd0f64a628204a4ad11b55","tid":391380,"uid":20182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T17:29:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大你兩年，就算俾你地一齊左，都好難一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"438462f93670b6f2580d46a888aefdecd1b781ec","tid":391380,"uid":22974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T17:29:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"062b8aa40ab2f24538c5391766f80482ad68883c","tid":391380,"uid":140357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T17:30:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大你兩年，就算俾你地一齊左，都好難一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇開始過,講咩一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bd760735768ce7793d9d4a9d68ee3c0d6df9295","tid":391380,"uid":90178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T17:30:19.000Z","msg":"呀，時也命也運也，非吾之所能slu"},{"pid":"b6e75b7efe91a4491e303ece45bd4dccbb88447e",